        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\npatchset 3 picks up the recently merged change that adds a chart for dcae-snmptrap-collector and modifies those charts to add the Consul key delete job.\ndcae-snmptrap-collector is not deployed by default in a DCAE Helm installation.  It's intended to be\ndeployed on demand after the initial deployment of ONAP and DCAE.  I verified that on-demand deployment and undeployment (via helm install and helm delete) works in my test environment.  The\nConsul delete job runs correctly during undeployment.",
